text: Nicolás Pizarro (born 29 September 1978) is a Mexican equestrian. He competed in two events at the 2012 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Mexico Category:Equestrians at the 2012 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Mexico City
